### Tier 1A: 对抗鲁棒性测试 ✅

**新文件**: [run_v39_adversarial_stress.py](file:///d:/cell/Morphosphere_v37_0_native_runtime_prototype_flat_complete.tar/Morphosphere_v37_0_native_runtime_prototype_flat_complete/Morphosphere_v37_0_native_runtime_prototype_flat_complete/morphosphere_v2pp/runners/run_v39_adversarial_stress.py)

| 攻击 | 结果 | 发现 |
|------|------|------|
| Xin 脉冲 (5.0 spike) | ✅ PASS | avg ΔW = 0.00497 |
| 慢爬攻击 (0→4.36) | ✅ PASS | 7/30 大变化 |
| 交替噪声 (high/low) | ✅ PASS | ΔW variance = 2.61e-07 |
| 持续低阈值 (0.3×50) | ✅ PASS | 33/50 大变化 |

